4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses the use of codes on graphs, which is a topic that is relevant to social and information networks. Graphical models and message passing algorithms are also commonly used in network analysis. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the use of iterative algorithms and codes, which are topics that are relevant to data structures and algorithms. The paper also discusses the efficiency of encoding algorithms, which is a topic that is relevant to algorithm design.
